songs.title: The End of All Things
songs.album: Too Weird to Live, Too Rare to Die!
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Whether near or far
I am always yours
Any change in time
We are young again

[Chorus]
Lay us down
We're in love
Lay us down
We're in love

[Verse 2]
In these coming years
Many things will change
But the way I feel
Will remain the same

[Chorus]
Lay us down
We're in love
Lay us down
We're in love
